					<li id="twitter"><a href="http://twitter.com/share?text=Library System plans Alderman renovation" data-url="http://cav.stage.getsnworks.com/article/2014/09/library-system-plans-alderman-renovation" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-twitter fa-lg"></i><span class="hidden-xs">Tweet</span></a></li>
